[I] A multi-platform support library with a focus on asynchronous I/O

[T] libuv is a multi-platform support library with a focus on asynchronous I/O.
[T] It was primarily developed for use by Node.js, but it's also used by Luvit,
[T] Julia, pyuv, and others.

